==English==
===Pronunciation===
*[[IPA]]: /nʌʧ/
===Etymology===
[[aphetic]] form of '''not much'''
===Expression===
'''nuch'''
# (''surfer slang'') a response to the greeting/question ''[[What's up]]''.
#: ''Dude! [[sup#Interjection|Sup]]? : '''Nuch'''.''
===Adverb===
'''nuch'''
# (''surfer slang'') not much, hardly, barely, to an insignificant degree.
